abstract: Experts say prevention is the best cure.
snippet: Experts say prevention is the best cure.
lead_paragraph: Road trips are never easy, but they are far more unpleasant when your child repeatedly vomits in the back seat because they’re carsick. I know, because that’s what happens whenever I drive more than an hour with my 8-year-old. She’s now had enough practice to neatly throw up into a plastic bag, but I feel for her every time it happens and wonder what I can do to ease her misery.

main: Why We Get Motion Sick, and How to Stop It
print_headline: Why We Get Motion Sickness, and How to Stop It

abstract: Moscow withdrew a key air defense system and some troops to bolster its war in Ukraine, officials said, potentially altering Israel’s calculations about striking Syria or arming Ukraine.
snippet: Moscow withdrew a key air defense system and some troops to bolster its war in Ukraine, officials said, potentially altering Israel’s calculations about striking Syria or arming Ukraine.
lead_paragraph: JERUSALEM — Russia recently redeployed critical military hardware and troops from Syria, according to three senior officials based in the Middle East, underscoring how its faltering invasion of Ukraine has eroded Moscow’s influence elsewhere and removing one of several obstacles to Israeli support for Ukraine.

main: Russia Shrinks Forces in Syria, a Factor in Israeli Strategy There
print_headline: Russia Transfers Forces to Ukraine From Syria, Affecting Strategy of Israel
